---
// Journey.astro - The Human Protocol
---

<section class="relative w-full py-32 bg-[#050505] text-white overflow-hidden font-sans">
  
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[60%] h-[60%] bg-orange-900/10 blur-[180px] rounded-full"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-32 space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-mono text-orange-500 uppercase tracking-[0.5em] reveal-text">Our_Lineage</h2>
      <h3 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase leading-none">
        Logic Meets <br/> <span class="text-orange-500">Empathy.</span>
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-xl mx-auto text-lg font-light leading-relaxed">
        We didn't choose this path because it was easy. We chose it because digital precision without human soul is just noise.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
      <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 top-0 w-[1px] h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-orange-500/50 via-white/10 to-transparent -translate-x-1/2"></div>

      <div class="space-y-24">
        
        <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between journey-item">
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] mb-8 md:mb-0 text-left md:text-right">
            <span class="text-orange-500 font-mono text-xs">Phase_01 // 2021</span>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase mt-2">The Digital Void</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              We noticed a world of cold, "perfect" websites that felt dead. Our journey began with a single question: <span class="text-white italic">"Where is the heartbeat?"</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3 h-3 bg-orange-500 rounded-full shadow-[0_0_15px_#f97316] z-20"></div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%]"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between journey-item">
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] order-2 md:order-1"></div>
          <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full z-20"></div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] order-1 md:order-2">
            <span class="text-orange-500 font-mono text-xs">The Pivot // 2023</span>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase mt-2">Human Centered Code</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              We developed the <strong class="text-white">G-Protocol</strong>. Not as a set of rules, but as a bridge. We chose minimalism to give your story space to breathe, and orange to give it the energy it deserves.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between journey-item">
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] text-left md:text-right">
            <span class="text-orange-500 font-mono text-xs">Today // Execution</span>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase mt-2">Meaningful Impact</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Every project we take on is a partnership. We don't just "build" for clients; we co-author their visual legacy. Our uniqueness lies in our <span class="text-white">obsession with your "Why."</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3 h-3 bg-orange-500 rounded-full shadow-[0_0_15px_#f97316] z-20"></div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%]"></div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-40 p-12 bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm text-center relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-orange-500/50 to-transparent"></div>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 italic">"Technology is just the tool. The connection is the art."</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto text-sm">
            Our journey isn't finished. It starts again with every project we initialize.
        </p>
        <button class="px-8 py-3 border border-orange-500 text-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-500 hover:text-black transition-all duration-300 font-bold uppercase text-[10px] tracking-widest">
            Join Our Story
        </button>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .journey-item {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(40px);
    transition: all 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .journey-item.active {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* Text balance for professional headers */
  h3 {
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
</style>

<script>
  const journeyObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        entry.target.classList.add('active');
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.3 });

  document.querySelectorAll('.journey-item').forEach(el => journeyObserver.observe(el));
</script>